{"tid":1430123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千奇唔好放棄每一個可以叫醒身邊既人既機會","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:01:59.000Z","uid":257398,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51a8a1d748985028fa13774bb7a02dd47ca7dde9","tid":1430123,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"6月到易家，兩個月了，當中一定有啲比較脆弱既巴絲已經覺得無力覺得攰覺得睇唔到希望，佢地需要停一停抖一抖。亦都有啲人港豬咗個幾月，居然有生之年見到佢地開始出下聲，終於出下聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個時候，呢班曾經港豬既人就可以補上，多一個得一個。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解會咁講？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為早排有港豬朋友俾人亂捉拘捕咗，佢放返出嚟之後就開始每日係story講，係一個好好既開始，喚醒咗要驅動就易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而佢既深藍家人、親戚同港豬朋友都開始關注，什至企出黎，即使唔係前線，但佢地每一個都好重要。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">成日係到諗捉撚晒啲港豬深藍入返48小時就好了哈哈</span>"},{"pid":"8b011b1a3fb107cc11370c7dd34b4b931fc3d088","tid":1430123,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"164eeb31acce2eebe8309f602b41d21d9377f9ad","tid":1430123,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"ae592646888e1745f8473140897b1b900ec5758c","tid":1430123,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"52bd11e0e1ff85ca5f21c8d1801492d4f539db7d","tid":1430123,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"44635f31650e6bb49d1927db049e1bbd69d793da","tid":1430123,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"b74e2216d63174cb1f5fb33f79dd43814a7b73ca","tid":1430123,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"178da6459febdae10c2513a556d466275a314092","tid":1430123,"uid":2